name: Adams Mitchell
body:
# Professional Profile
Over seven years experience working in the IT field at Aiken Technical College.  Started full-time as an Applications Analyst whose duties included maintaining all websites belonging to ATC (including coding and IIS management), maintaining and accessing related SQL databases, incorporating SSL certificates on all related servers, and the creation of SSIS projects which create data feeds used by third-party company sites.

# Code Experience
* HTML (4 - 5), CSS, Javascript - 7-8 years
* MySQL, MSSQL - 7 years
* ASP.NET (2.0, 3.0, 3.5) - 6 years
* VB.NET - 6 years
* IIS administration - 5 years
* AJAX for ASP.NET - 5 years
* SSIS - 5 years
* Adobe Suites (Web Development, Photoshop, Illustrator) 4 - 5 years
* Sharepoint administration - 3 years
* PHP - 2 years
